    <p>The vegan gummy candy market has exploded. What used to mean "tasteless health food" now includes brands that rival — and in many cases beat — traditional gelatin-based candy in flavor, texture, and overall satisfaction. The shift is driven by two forces: consumer demand for plant-based products and genuine ingredient innovation. Pectin-based formulations have matured to the point where most people cannot distinguish vegan gummies from conventional ones in blind tastings. We purchased and tested over 25 vegan gummy candy products to identify the 8 that deserve your money.</p>

