    <p>Surf Sweets (a brand under TCHO / WholeMe Foods) is the go-to vegan gummy for parents who want the cleanest possible ingredient list. Their Organic Fruity Bears are made with real organic fruit juice as a primary flavoring ingredient — not just fruit "flavoring." The allergen-free formulation is critical for school snack policies that ban common allergens. Every color comes from organic vegetable and fruit concentrates with zero synthetic dyes. The texture is slightly softer than conventional gummies due to the tapioca starch and pectin blend, but kids consistently rate the taste as their favorite in our testing panels.</p>

